txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Gilded sword sheaths from the Orcs and Angmarim from the lands surrounding Aughaire. Deliver the items to Raith at Aughaire in the south-western reaches of Angmar.
'We shall sheath our weapons within these now. Thank you.'
'Our oppressors taunt us with opulent sheaths for their vicious weapons. We shall bear them instead in battle.'
Council of the North Task: Gilded Sword Sheaths
The Hillmen at Aughaire have requested a collection of gilded sword sheaths to be delivered to Raith.
Deliver the gilded sword sheaths to Raith at Aughaire in Angmar
You have accepted a task to collect and deliver gilded sword sheaths from the Orcs and Angmarim surrounding Aughaire to Raith, a Hillman within the settlement.
Wanted: Gilded sword sheaths from the Orcs and Angmarim from the lands surrounding Aughaire.
